hopobject.body: I'd like to tell you about a change of address hair loss recovery time Pharmaceutical turnover edged up 1% to $7.89 billion, hit by a 14% decline in sales of the blood pressure lowerer Diovan (valsartan) to $835 million, due to generic competition in Europe. Although off-patent in the USA, Novartis is still benefitting from the fact that the Food and Drug Administration has yet to approve any competitor for Diovan monotherapy.
